description:
InContact enables you to quickly call, email, IM, or TXT your frequently used contacts with only 2 taps.  Features:
- draggable photos to reorder display,
- automatic or user selected phone number, IM name, or email address,
- selection of 6 themes,
- selection of default, transparent, and "phone" launcher icons,
- close on dial or any other action,
- support for portrait & landscape display modes,
- icons to launch the Palm dialer, email, messaging and contact applications, and
- a new "Driving Mode" with larger icons that are easier to find and tap.

Available in: English, Spanish.
